Class RoomBookingRepo_JPAH2

java.lang.Object
com.itkolleg.bookingsystem.repos.roombooking.RoomBookingRepo_JPAH2

RoomBookingRepo
@Component @ComponentScan("com.itkolleg.repos") public class RoomBookingRepo_JPAH2 extends Object implements RoomBookingRepo
The RoomBookingRepo_JPAH2 class is responsible for managing room bookings in the booking system using JPA and H2 database.
